webpackJsonp([380],{"./node_modules/json-loader/index.js!./.cache/json/articles-miscellaneous-getting-a-coding-job.json":function(e,o){e.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<p>Free Code Camp will help you prepare for a coding job.</p>\n<div class="lightbox-wrapper">[![](https://www.evernote.com/shard/s116/sh/55c128c7-5d99-41cc-b03d-b3de22611c8d/b43e467b3889f646fec34bb4c161e2a2/deep/0/What\'s-wrong-with-this-picture----Code.org.png)\n<div class="meta"><span class="filename">What\'s-wrong-with-this-picture----Code.org.png</span><span class="informations">698x528</span><span class="expand"></span></div>](https://www.evernote.com/shard/s116/sh/55c128c7-5d99-41cc-b03d-b3de22611c8d/b43e467b3889f646fec34bb4c161e2a2/deep/0/What\'s-wrong-with-this-picture----Code.org.png "What\'s-wrong-with-this-picture----Code.org.png") </div>\n<h2>Here are the facts:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>There are hundreds of thousands of unfilled coding jobs.</li>\n<li>Employers and the US government have joined together to promote nontraditional coding programs like Free Code Camp.</li>\n<li>Full stack JavaScript is one of the best paying skill sets, and has a ton of job openings.</li>\n<li>The best proof that you\'re an employable developer is a portfolio filled with real apps that real people are using.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You\'ll still need to develop basic interviewing skills and soft skills (if you\'ve been working a knowledge-worker type job for a few years, you probably already have these).</p>\n<p>You\'ll also need to work hard to network with coders in your city. You can do this by joining <a href="https://github.com/FreeCodeCamp/FreeCodeCamp/wiki/LocalGroups-List">your city\'s Local Group</a> and participating in as many events as possible.</p>\n<p>I\'ve found <a href="https://github.com/cassidoo/getting-a-gig">this</a> link to be useful. It does a great job of explaining the process.</p>',frontmatter:{title:"Getting a Coding Job",parent:"/home/stuart/guides/src/pages/articles/miscellaneous/getting-a-coding-job/index.md absPath of file"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/articles/miscellaneous/getting-a-coding-job/"}}}});
